creator: Susan Coolidge
description:
LibriVox recording of Verses by Susan Coolidge.
Read in English by Rachel; Urban Bard; Larry Wilson; Kathleen Moore; Ezwa; Crystal Gattis; LisaRubio; Gloria Begemann; Sonia; Eric Burns; Joe Brenneman; Dillon McFarlane; Greg Giordano; jmoon110; Roohi; Gemma Domenella; John Burlinson; SkyAlbatross
Susan Coolidge was the pen name of Sarah Chauncey Woolsey, who is best known for her What Katy Did series. This is the first of three volumes of her verse. (Summary by Rachel)
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
